title: Darkest Africa (1936) Old Time Serial (OTS)
description:

A 15-episode serial in which Beatty goes to darkest Africa to rescue the Goddess of Joba, who is being held by the high priest.

Directors: B. Reeves Eason, Joseph Kane

Writers: John Rathmell (screenplay), Barney A. Sarecky (screenplay)

Stars: Clyde Beatty, Manuel King, Elaine Shepard
